  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - LII. In Caecilianum.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Si tibi per genium fas est jurare Minervae,</l>
     <l n="2">Per Veneris flavas, Caeciliane, comas,</l>
     <l n="3">Nec jubar excipitur Solis, nec cornua Phoebes,</l>
     <l n="4">Nec Capitolini crura, caputque Patris:</l>
     <l n="5">Cur mihi tu ventrem, cur intestina Deorum,</l>
     <l n="6">Hispana tactus relligione, sonas?</l>
     <l n="7">Non pudet heu caelum rebus foedare pudendis?</l>
     <l n="8">An credis magnos haec quoque habere Deos?</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
